Scarlet Heart
Episode 19

24
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:21,020
[ Royal Throne ]

25
00:02:28,780 --> 00:02:30,540
Do you want it?

26
00:02:34,220 --> 00:02:36,140
You don't have to answer.

27
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:37,340
I do.

28
00:02:37,780 --> 00:02:39,580
Have you told anyone?

29
00:02:39,580 --> 00:02:40,660
You're the first one.

30
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:42,460
What about 13th Prince?

31
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,860
13th Prince and I grew up together.

32
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:48,060
What I am thinking can't be hidden from him.

33
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:50,060
I don't need to tell him.

34
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:51,960
Aren't you scared

35
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:54,160
that I'll tell others?

36
00:02:58,580 --> 00:03:01,040
The bet you placed was too big.

37
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:03,500
Although I didn't want to gamble,

38
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:08,160
I was afraid that if I missed this chance,

39
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,480
you'd keep your heart

40
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:11,020
closed too tightly.

41
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,200
If I missed this chance,

42
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:16,580
I didn't know if there would be another one.

43
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:23,260
Telling others

44
00:03:24,220 --> 00:03:25,740
you wouldn't do.

45
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:29,560
Even the Emperor was never suspicious of you.

46
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:32,520
Why are you telling me now?

47
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:34,600
Am I hallucinating?

48
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:38,000
All right.

49
00:03:38,980 --> 00:03:40,840
Then let me ask you.

50
00:03:46,060 --> 00:03:47,340
What does 4th prince wish to know?

51
00:03:50,380 --> 00:03:51,960
I want to know,

52
00:03:53,100 --> 00:03:55,320
did that kick hurt?

53
00:03:56,460 --> 00:03:58,060
Scared me again.

54
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,380
It doesn't hurt, but it isn't a light injury.

55
00:04:01,620 --> 00:04:03,240
It is a mild pain.

56
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,480
Yutan has already helped me apply medicine.

57
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,540
It's not a big deal.

58
00:04:11,900 --> 00:04:13,060
This medicine,

59
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:15,400
use it once every morning and night.

60
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,980
It won't affect the medicine you've applied externally.

61
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:21,460
By the way,

62
00:04:21,460 --> 00:04:23,140
what did Imperial Father say to you

63
00:04:23,340 --> 00:04:24,860
to turn you so strange?

64
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,279
You didn't even greet us when you saw us.

65
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:29,340
Yesterday, His Majesty asked to see me

66
00:04:29,380 --> 00:04:31,900
to ask why 10th Prince and Fujin were fighting

67
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:33,600
and

68
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,520
how I advised 10th prince.

69
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,200
Later,

70
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,880
His Majesty said something

71
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:41,560
I don't understand.

72
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,960
What did he say?

73
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:46,020
He asked me

74
00:04:46,020 --> 00:04:48,100
if in the future, can I

75
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:49,840
forget what I have lost

76
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:51,300
and value what I have.

77
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:54,460
How did you answer?

78
00:04:54,980 --> 00:04:59,120
I said I didn't know.

79
00:05:00,020 --> 00:05:02,120
Before I understand what His Majesty is thinking,

80
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:04,040
I can only say that

81
00:05:04,060 --> 00:05:05,880
I think

82
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:09,400
Imperial Father thinks you like 13th Brother.

83
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:11,620
Is it because of the time

84
00:05:11,620 --> 00:05:13,500
I competed with Minmin?

85
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:15,080
Probably is.

86
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:17,980
Minmin's reactions to 13th Brother

87
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:19,140
were so strange,

88
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:21,320
Imperial Father would connect it

89
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:22,900
to a relationship between lovers.

90
00:05:24,980 --> 00:05:26,760
What did Guwalgiya Wang'ye

91
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,600
say to His Majesty

92
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:31,440
so that His Majesty did not pursue the matter?

93
00:05:33,140 --> 00:05:34,940
Didn't you wonder before?

94
00:05:36,340 --> 00:05:38,640
Wang'ye would definitely tell His Majesty the truth

95
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:40,640
about Minmin's feelings for 13th Prince.

96
00:05:40,940 --> 00:05:42,040
But afterward,

97
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,420
he must have said something

98
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:44,480
about not letting Minmin

99
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:46,340
marry 13th Prince

100
00:05:46,340 --> 00:05:48,120
and convinced His Majesty

101
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:50,780
to agree to Minmin and Prince Zuoying.

102
00:05:51,460 --> 00:05:52,980
As to why His Majesty would

103
00:05:52,980 --> 00:05:55,720
allow Minmin and Prince Zuoying,

104
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,240
not only do I not understand,

105
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:59,280
I think it was a mistake.

106
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:01,900
It's all right for His Majesty to allow the marriage between the two tribes,

107
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:05,620
but he also secretly supported Prince Zuoying to fight for his inheritance.

108
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:07,320
Yinerganzhuluo's 1st Prince's

109
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,780
twin sister

110
00:06:08,780 --> 00:06:11,000
is Nalanbu's new Imperial concubine.

111
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,960
Do you understand now?

112
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:15,260
I understand

113
00:06:15,260 --> 00:06:17,220
to even out the power of the tribes

114
00:06:17,220 --> 00:06:18,820
by letting them fight

115
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:20,320
amongst themselves.

116
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,340
In the end, no one will be in command.

117
00:06:22,340 --> 00:06:23,500
Correct.

118
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:25,320
This is why Imperial Father

119
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:29,020
agreed with Minmin and Prince Zuoying's marriage.

120
00:06:30,300 --> 00:06:31,680
It's too complicated.

121
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,820
I just know that Minmin marrying 13th Prince

122
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:36,500
is more advantageous than her marrying Prince Zuoying.

123
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:38,360
Do you think

124
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,660
the Emperor is wrong?

125
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,940
Years ago,

126
00:06:40,940 --> 00:06:42,620
people said I fancied 10th Prince

127
00:06:42,620 --> 00:06:45,840
Now, they say I fancy the 13th Prince.

128
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:46,760
I don't think

129
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:48,200
you would fancy 10th Brother.

130
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,420
But

131
00:06:49,420 --> 00:06:50,900
I'm surprised

132
00:06:50,900 --> 00:06:52,240
you don't fancy 13th Brother.

133
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:55,480
His Majesty's words

134
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,780
aren't they

135
00:06:56,780 --> 00:06:58,400
to grant my wish

136
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,000
or not?

137
00:07:00,220 --> 00:07:01,920
Ruoxi,

138
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:03,980
Imperial Father really dotes on you.

139
00:07:03,980 --> 00:07:06,380
From what you're saying, Imperial Father's words

140
00:07:06,380 --> 00:07:08,020
in any event relating to you, he is really

141
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:09,280
hesitating.

142
00:07:10,620 --> 00:07:13,440
He really cares for how you feel.

143
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:19,640
Then, in the future, would His Majesty agree?

144
00:07:24,180 --> 00:07:25,580
Shy?

145
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:28,520
No.

146
00:07:43,100 --> 00:07:45,500
After the Crown Prince's incident settles down

147
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:47,840
I'll ask Imperial Father.

148
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:50,860
I think that with our feelings,

149
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:53,260
he will agree.

150
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:55,760
Don't waste energy

151
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:57,320
wondering about these things.

152
00:07:57,780 --> 00:08:00,100
Although your marriage is a bit problematic,

153
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:00,940
as long as

154
00:08:00,940 --> 00:08:02,940
it doesn't involve taking the throne,

155
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:04,000
I believe that Imperial Father

156
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,480
will let us be together.

157
00:08:06,140 --> 00:08:07,700
If you really have time,

158
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:10,140
then think about something meaningful.

159
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:14,060
Then, what is it, that's meaningful?

160
00:08:15,580 --> 00:08:17,940
For example, for my birthday

161
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:19,780
what song will you sing to me

162
00:08:19,780 --> 00:08:22,640
and what song will you dance to for me to see.

163
00:08:24,260 --> 00:08:25,700
Since Wang'ye has ordered it,

164
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:27,740
how can I not obey.

165
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:32,260
Who is it?

166
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:34,520
Your servant, Fang He.

167
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,400
What?

168
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,579
14th Prince ordered me to send medicine.

169
00:08:46,579 --> 00:08:49,120
The instructions are inside.

170
00:08:57,460 --> 00:09:00,000
Did 14th brother send it?

171
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:04,060
You have to leave?

172
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:07,940
After Crown Prince asked for you hand in marriage,

173
00:09:07,940 --> 00:09:09,820
you have been distracted.

174
00:09:09,820 --> 00:09:11,860
I thought you were getting better,

175
00:09:12,860 --> 00:09:14,480
now, one word from Imperial Father

176
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,560
has caused you to be strange again.

177
00:09:17,740 --> 00:09:19,060
I think

178
00:09:19,060 --> 00:09:20,540
from now on,

179
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:22,420
there will be quite a few problems.

180
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,900
Will you face them looking like this?

181
00:09:29,180 --> 00:09:30,640
The more your heart is afraid,

182
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,940
the more your face has to remain calm.

183
00:09:32,940 --> 00:09:34,700
If others can't figure you out,

184
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:37,220
they won't easily make any moves.

185
00:09:39,260 --> 00:09:41,020
Who would be like you

186
00:09:42,620 --> 00:09:45,480
and wear their emotions on their sleeve?

187
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:48,820
I'll remember.

188
00:09:48,820 --> 00:09:50,340
Then I'll leave.

189
00:09:56,580 --> 00:09:58,380
I'll take this as evidence

190
00:09:59,340 --> 00:10:02,060
to see if you've improved next time.

191
00:10:08,220 --> 00:10:09,820
10th Prince! 10th Prince!

192
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:11,320
What?

193
00:10:11,940 --> 00:10:12,820
Say it quickly.

194
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:14,016
When is Fu'jin coming back?

195
00:10:14,016 --> 00:10:15,100
Replying to 10th Prince,

196
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:16,420
10th Fujin wasn't willing to see me.

197
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:17,920
She told someone to tell me

198
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,340
that she will not return.

199
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:21,680
It was just a lantern!

200
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:23,340
Is it worth having such a big fight over?

201
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,160
10th Fujin said,

202
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:27,260
if 10th Prince wants her to return,

203
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:28,060
you will have to--

204
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:29,480
Have to do what? Say it fast!

205
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:31,100
You have to apologize to her.

206
00:10:31,100 --> 00:10:32,260
What?

207
00:10:32,260 --> 00:10:33,780
She wants me to apologize to her?

208
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:35,440
What a scandal!

209
00:10:36,060 --> 00:10:38,000
Then do I have to kneel to her too?

210
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,480
If she doesn't want to come back, then don't come back!

211
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:41,900
I don't care!

212
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:44,080
I'll tell you,

213
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:46,300
I do like candied haw and hate hibiscus cake!

214
00:10:46,300 --> 00:10:47,860
So what!

215
00:10:48,740 --> 00:10:50,820
You! Return home

216
00:10:50,820 --> 00:10:51,880
and tell her,

217
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:54,060
if she doesn't come back, I'll...

218
00:10:54,180 --> 00:10:56,320
I'll ask for an edict to divorce the hibiscus cake!

219
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:58,100
Why aren't you gone yet?

220
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:59,700
No, I'm afraid I heard wrong,

221
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:01,860
did 10th Prince just say to divorce a hibiscus cake?

222
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:04,500
I... I said to divorce Fujin!

223
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:06,540
Why are you still standing here? Hurry and Go!

224
00:11:06,540 --> 00:11:08,100
Yes.

225
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:10,860
How dare she?

226
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:14,560
I will go buy all the candied haws in the city.

227
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:17,420
I'll... I'll... I'll anger you to death!

228
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:22,760
How dare she?

229
00:11:22,980 --> 00:11:26,760
He dares?! How dare him! Howdare him!

230
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:28,480
Having a tantrum here,

231
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,980
10th Prince can't see it.

232
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:33,800
If you want to be angry, be angry at home. It only works if 10th Prince sees it

233
00:11:33,800 --> 00:11:35,180
I don't want to return!

234
00:11:35,180 --> 00:11:37,100
He wants to bring me back and just sent a servant!

235
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:38,980
He doesn't have any sincerity.

236
00:11:38,980 --> 00:11:40,820
If I return like this,

237
00:11:40,820 --> 00:11:41,860
then in 10th Prince's estate,

238
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:43,960
how will I have control?

239
00:11:45,140 --> 00:11:47,420
Your pacing is making me dizzy.

240
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:51,300
No matter what 10th Prince says, he's still a prince.

241
00:11:51,300 --> 00:11:52,640
You have to give him some face.

242
00:11:53,220 --> 00:11:54,500
He has to have face, but I can't?

243
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:56,240
He's the one not giving me face!

244
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,020
And made me hate the Lantern Festival,

245
00:11:58,020 --> 00:12:00,080
which was originally my favorite holiday!

246
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:02,240
It was just a lantern,

247
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,640
what can it represent?

248
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:05,340
I see a lantern now,

249
00:12:05,340 --> 00:12:06,180
but behind it

250
00:12:06,180 --> 00:12:08,220
is a fire dragon!

251
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:09,660
Informing mistresses,

252
00:12:09,660 --> 00:12:12,020
Tenth Prince's Xiao An Zi is here to pass a message along.

253
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:13,120
Let him come in.

254
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,400
Yes.

255
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:18,500
Since Tenth Prince sent someone to pass a message,

256
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:20,220
give him some face

257
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:22,620
and stop playing tricks.

258
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:27,460
Greetings, 8th Fujin.

259
00:12:27,460 --> 00:12:28,620
Greetings, 10th Fujin.

260
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:30,040
Rise.

261
00:12:30,520 --> 00:12:32,240
What did 10th Prince say?

262
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,340
10th Prince said...

263
00:12:33,340 --> 00:12:35,940
if 10th Fujin doesn't return,

264
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:38,120
he will... will...

265
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:40,180
will divorce 10th Fujin.

266
00:12:41,260 --> 00:12:42,220
What?!

267
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,800
Jie'jie,

268
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:47,840
you hear that?

269
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:49,780
Did he only say this?

270
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:51,700
Yes.

271
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:54,580
Then when you returned earlier with Mingyu's message,

272
00:12:54,700 --> 00:12:56,120
what was 10th Prince's reaction?

273
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:57,940
He was a little upset

274
00:12:57,940 --> 00:13:00,320
saying something about liking candied haws

275
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,540
and disliking hibiscus cakes.

276
00:13:03,820 --> 00:13:05,380
