00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:00,340
Mingyu,

563
00:25:01,580 --> 00:25:02,500
as long as our hearts

564
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:04,120
are together

565
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:07,020
no one can separate us.

566
00:25:22,700 --> 00:25:25,700
Mingyu, don't worry,

567
00:25:25,720 --> 00:25:27,040
as long as, in front of the Imperial Father we show

568
00:25:27,040 --> 00:25:28,920
that we are in love

569
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:30,020
and respect each other,

570
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:31,320
Imperial Father

571
00:25:31,420 --> 00:25:33,040
won't separate us.

572
00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:34,620
But...

573
00:25:34,900 --> 00:25:36,840
But if it's already been decided that

574
00:25:36,940 --> 00:25:37,780
Imperial Father is forcing me to marry

575
00:25:37,780 --> 00:25:39,400
that Persian Prince,

576
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:41,440
then what are we going to do?

577
00:25:42,040 --> 00:25:43,900
If it is like this...

578
00:25:44,580 --> 00:25:45,580
if it is like this,

579
00:25:45,700 --> 00:25:46,900
I don't want to live anymore.

580
00:25:46,900 --> 00:25:48,900
I'll elope with you!

581
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:50,940
Really?

582
00:25:51,380 --> 00:25:52,480
Yes.

583
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:55,280
Mingyu,

584
00:25:55,380 --> 00:25:56,940
are you afraid of dying?

585
00:26:00,860 --> 00:26:02,600
If I am with you,

586
00:26:02,700 --> 00:26:03,960
even if we go to the land of the dead together,

587
00:26:04,060 --> 00:26:05,880
I will be happy.

588
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:23,020
Are you ready?

589
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,960
10th Brother, 10th Sister-in-law,

590
00:26:46,080 --> 00:26:48,020
are you going to see Imperial Father?

591
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:51,220
How did you know?

592
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:54,020
It must be those servants!

593
00:26:54,460 --> 00:26:56,680
They wanted to share their master's troubles.

594
00:26:57,100 --> 00:26:57,960
However,

595
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,880
you don't need to go anymore.

596
00:26:59,980 --> 00:27:01,180
But you can still make it...

597
00:27:01,180 --> 00:27:02,140
otherwise, Ruoxi

598
00:27:02,140 --> 00:27:04,080
will definitely get punished by Imperial Father.

599
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:07,380
What do you mean?

600
00:27:07,740 --> 00:27:08,800
Actually, Imperial Father

601
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:09,620
doesn't know a thing

602
00:27:09,620 --> 00:27:11,840
about the fight between you two.

603
00:27:12,020 --> 00:27:12,840
But Ruoxi

604
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:14,060
clearly told me

605
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:15,500
she already told Imperial Father

606
00:27:15,500 --> 00:27:16,780
about our fight.

607
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:17,640
That's right,

608
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:19,460
didn't Imperial Father already look for my father

609
00:27:19,620 --> 00:27:20,860
to discuss

610
00:27:20,860 --> 00:27:23,000
us breaking up?

611
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:25,660
Ruoxi made it all up.

612
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:27,860
Should I believe you

613
00:27:27,860 --> 00:27:30,060
or Ruoxi?

614
00:27:31,620 --> 00:27:33,620
Let's believe 14th Brother.

615
00:27:37,300 --> 00:27:37,940
Oh, no wonder you said

616
00:27:37,940 --> 00:27:39,280
Ruoxi is going to be punished.

617
00:27:39,380 --> 00:27:39,860
But why did she

618
00:27:39,860 --> 00:27:41,520
say such things?

619
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:43,940
Almost ruined us as a couple.

620
00:27:43,940 --> 00:27:45,280
Causing us to be separated.

621
00:27:45,380 --> 00:27:46,480
That is because--

622
00:27:46,580 --> 00:27:48,500
However, she thinks is fine.

623
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:52,620
Since we don't have to see Imperial Father anymore,

624
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:54,780
let's go home.

625
00:28:00,280 --> 00:28:01,720
10th Brother, 10th Sister-in-law,

626
00:28:02,480 --> 00:28:03,940
I have never seen

627
00:28:03,940 --> 00:28:05,180
you holding each other's hands

628
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:07,200
this tightly before.

629
00:28:12,340 --> 00:28:14,460
Wait for me downstairs.

630
00:28:14,460 --> 00:28:15,920
Make it fast.

631
00:28:20,740 --> 00:28:21,520
14th Prince,

632
00:28:21,620 --> 00:28:24,140
may I trouble you to convey a message to Ruoxi.

633
00:28:24,260 --> 00:28:25,180
Of course.

634
00:28:26,740 --> 00:28:28,100
I know what she did

635
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:29,340
was to use a shock tactic

636
00:28:29,340 --> 00:28:31,720
to make me reconcile with 10th Prince.

637
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:32,660
But she mustn't expect me to thank

638
00:28:32,660 --> 00:28:34,360
her for that.

639
00:28:34,460 --> 00:28:35,660
Because happiness

640
00:28:35,740 --> 00:28:37,640
needs one's own effort to get it.

641
00:28:37,740 --> 00:28:39,880
I am sure, she knows that herself.

642
00:28:39,980 --> 00:28:41,740
She knows.

643
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:50,100
Let's go!

644
00:28:56,560 --> 00:28:57,640
8th Brother,

645
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:59,600
only Ruoxi herself knows

646
00:28:59,700 --> 00:29:01,260
what her happiness is.

647
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:25,080
She has chosen to be with 4th Prince.

648
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,240
10th Prince,

649
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:55,280
let's go.

650
00:31:56,840 --> 00:31:57,880
This flower's fragrance is really good.

651
00:31:57,880 --> 00:31:59,720
Because it's me who picked it.

652
00:31:59,740 --> 00:32:00,680
10th Prince, 10th Sister-in-law.

653
00:32:00,780 --> 00:32:02,280
14th Brother.

654
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:04,920
Greetings, 14th Prince.

655
00:32:05,020 --> 00:32:06,340
Rise.

656
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:08,740
10th Brother and 10th Sister-in-law are really teasing together.

657
00:32:08,940 --> 00:32:10,240
Both suddenly changed.

658
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:11,080
Before, with only a short conversation

659
00:32:11,180 --> 00:32:12,400
and they'd already get into a fight.

660
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:13,440
Now when they see each other,

661
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,340
they go to great lengths to dote on each other.

662
00:32:15,540 --> 00:32:16,940
Not like the way they were in their first year of marriage.

663
00:32:17,140 --> 00:32:18,140
They seem like a couple

664
00:32:18,140 --> 00:32:19,740
of young newlyweds.

665
00:32:20,380 --> 00:32:21,520
Really can't imagine

666
00:32:21,620 --> 00:32:22,960
that such a hot-headed person

667
00:32:23,060 --> 00:32:25,420
would one day change into a compliant person.

668
00:32:29,760 --> 00:32:31,400
Ruoxi, by the way

669
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:32,680
I already give the bracelet

670
00:32:32,820 --> 00:32:35,040
to 8th Brother at his manor.

671
00:32:35,840 --> 00:32:38,300
8th brother accepted the bracelet with a smile.

672
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:40,820
He took the ink stone on his desk

673
00:32:40,820 --> 00:32:42,780
and broke the bracelet into pieces.

674
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:45,240
8th Brother laughed and said,

675
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:46,580
"In the end,

676
00:32:46,580 --> 00:32:48,520
she still chose 4th Brother."

677
00:32:48,620 --> 00:32:51,860
Ruoxi, is that true?

678
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:55,060
You didn't ask him

679
00:32:55,060 --> 00:32:57,440
why he said that?

680
00:32:57,540 --> 00:32:58,960
8th Brother said,

681
00:32:58,960 --> 00:33:00,780
since you entered the palace,

682
00:33:00,820 --> 00:33:03,400
you treat 4th Brother different from us others.

683
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:05,560
When serving tea,

684
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:07,920
it is firstly according to his preferences.

685
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:08,680
Then gradually

686
00:33:08,680 --> 00:33:10,740
to suit the taste of each other,

687
00:33:11,180 --> 00:33:12,200
in a lot of things,

688
00:33:12,300 --> 00:33:14,100
you tried your best to protect him.

689
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:16,440
You even splashed tea on 10th Brother.

690
00:33:17,700 --> 00:33:19,620
During year 47, when the Crown Prince was deposed,

691
00:33:20,060 --> 00:33:21,480
when you returned from Saiwai

692
00:33:22,140 --> 00:33:22,940
the expression in your eyes when you saw 4th Brother

693
00:33:22,940 --> 00:33:24,340
became more and more different.

694
00:33:25,100 --> 00:33:28,020
Sometimes your face would flush.

695
00:33:28,580 --> 00:33:30,420
Later, even without 8th Brother pointing it out to me,

696
00:33:30,420 --> 00:33:31,340
I noticed many times

697
00:33:31,340 --> 00:33:33,340
you and 4th Brother would flirt together.

698
00:33:33,340 --> 00:33:35,200
You sometimes smiled,

699
00:33:35,300 --> 00:33:37,060
sometimes you showed a little annoyance.

700
00:33:37,140 --> 00:33:37,900
but 8th Brother constantly paid attention to

701
00:33:37,900 --> 00:33:39,240
your every action.

702
00:33:39,340 --> 00:33:41,640
Normally, he would notice much more.

703
00:33:42,140 --> 00:33:43,540
I really didn't know,

704
00:33:44,180 --> 00:33:46,820
that this is what he thought from start to end.

705
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:48,920
That is because he never showed

706
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:50,800
his real thoughts.

707
00:33:51,180 --> 00:33:54,440
He never really trusted me.

708
00:33:54,940 --> 00:33:55,920
Ruoxi.

709
00:33:56,020 --> 00:33:57,540
Do you really love 4th Brother?

710
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:03,840
Yes.

711
00:34:03,840 --> 00:34:05,560
I love 4th Prince.

712
00:34:05,660 --> 00:34:07,800
I have always liked 4th Prince

713
00:34:07,900 --> 00:34:10,140
and love him deeply.

714
00:34:10,140 --> 00:34:12,840
Satisfied?

715
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,280
What's wong

716
00:34:25,519 --> 00:34:27,120
there is a tiger chasing you?

717
00:34:38,579 --> 00:34:40,080
What's wrong?

718
00:34:53,180 --> 00:34:54,959
From now on,

719
00:34:55,059 --> 00:34:57,420
you're not going to lie to me anymore?

720
00:34:57,900 --> 00:34:59,786
You'll tell me everything?

721
00:35:00,619 --> 00:35:02,080
Yes.

722
00:35:05,140 --> 00:35:06,820
I am fine.

723
00:35:09,780 --> 00:35:11,980
Want to know why?

724
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,740
There is something.

725
00:35:17,600 --> 00:35:19,460
I don't want to say it now,

726
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:22,620
can I not?

727
00:35:24,500 --> 00:35:26,160
Yes.

728
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:31,006
Imperial Father is still waiting for me

729
00:35:31,006 --> 00:35:32,680
and Thirteenth Brother.

730
00:35:32,900 --> 00:35:34,761
I'm leaving now.

731
00:35:43,420 --> 00:35:44,854
In the Forbidden City

732
00:35:44,854 --> 00:35:47,120
I am not alone.

733
00:35:47,120 --> 00:35:51,080
4th prince is willing to listen to my fears, worries, and troubles.

734
00:35:51,080 --> 00:35:53,680
He always reminds me of unforeseen dangers.

735
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:56,620
He opens himself to me.

736
00:35:56,620 --> 00:35:58,429
I don't know how it will be in the future,

737
00:35:58,529 --> 00:35:59,915
but at least for now

738
00:36:00,015 --> 00:36:02,794
it's a good beginning.

739
00:36:23,620 --> 00:36:25,860
Weren't you always avoiding me?

740
00:36:25,860 --> 00:36:28,420
How come you suddenly want to see me?

741
00:36:29,300 --> 00:36:30,457
I've thought for a long time.

742
00:36:31,420 --> 00:36:32,853
There are some things,

743
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:36,700
I still have to talk to you about.

744
00:36:38,820 --> 00:36:41,140
I am not an ideal person,

745
00:36:41,540 --> 00:36:44,220
but I always expect 8th Prince to be perfect.

746
00:36:44,660 --> 00:36:46,860
If my arrogance is tamed,

747
00:36:46,860 --> 00:36:48,900
my passion dies.

748
00:36:49,780 --> 00:36:51,842
If I was more resigned to fate,

749
00:36:51,842 --> 00:36:53,700
had more tolerance,

750
00:36:53,700 --> 00:36:55,880
was more forgiving,

751
00:36:55,980 --> 00:36:58,380
and had less prejudice,

752
00:36:58,831 --> 00:37:00,596
perhaps me and 8th Prince

753
00:37:00,596 --> 00:37:03,180
would have had a different ending.

754
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:08,720
You may think that I'm being truthful or...

755
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:10,636
I'm faking this.

756
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:13,794
But all this is over now.

757
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:16,461
Everything is like that jade bangle,

758
00:37:17,140 --> 00:37:19,480
regardless of its past glory

759
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:21,588
and beauty,

760
00:37:22,140 --> 00:37:24,414
it has already become dust.

761
00:37:26,951 --> 00:37:28,594
I'm really happy

762
00:37:29,700 --> 00:37:31,980
that you can speak frankly with me.

763
00:37:31,980 --> 00:37:34,861
I am only passing through your life.

764
00:37:35,705 --> 00:37:38,073
I don't ask to be forgiven,

765
00:37:38,328 --> 00:37:40,915
only want to wish to 8th prince

766
00:37:41,820 --> 00:37:43,908
will take good care of yourself.

767
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:46,494
You have care too.

768
00:38:02,020 --> 00:38:02,913
Li Dequan.

769
00:38:02,913 --> 00:38:03,600
Your Majesty.

770
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:06,680
How long since Ruoxi bothered to make something?

771
00:38:06,780 --> 00:38:07,618
Half a year.

772
00:38:07,618 --> 00:38:08,450
This year,

773
00:38:08,450 --> 00:38:11,765
I want to see what kinds of new things she's thought of.

774
00:38:22,420 --> 00:38:24,606
It has a clear and shiny color.

775
00:38:24,606 --> 00:38:26,201
The taste is not too sweet.

776
00:38:26,301 --> 00:38:27,919
It melts in the mouth.

777
00:38:28,019 --> 00:38:31,000
It even exudes the light fragrance of the lotus.

778
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,400
Not bad.

779
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:34,620
Thank you for your praise, Your Majesty.

780
00:38:34,620 --> 00:38:35,953
Let them taste it too.

781
00:38:36,053 --> 00:38:37,171
Yes.

782
00:38:56,200 --> 00:38:57,710
How's the taste?

783
00:38:57,810 --> 00:38:59,440
Exactly like what you said, Imperial Father.

784
00:38:59,540 --> 00:39:00,760
Yes, tastes good.

785
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:01,795
It melts in my mouth and...

786
00:39:01,795 --> 00:39:03,160
leaves a nice taste.

787
00:39:03,160 --> 00:39:04,317
4th Prince,

788
00:39:04,317 --> 00:39:05,818
what do you think?

789
00:39:12,940 --> 00:39:14,500
I think it's very good.

790
00:39:14,500 --> 00:39:15,706
I'm still savoring the taste.

791
00:39:15,806 --> 00:39:18,663
That's why I cannot answer you just now.

792
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:34,380
Bring one more.

793
00:39:48,140 --> 00:39:49,240
Where's 4th Prince?

794
00:39:49,340 --> 00:39:51,313
He went to change his clothes.

795
00:39:55,040 --> 00:39:57,650
What makes you so overjoyed, Rouxi?

796
00:39:58,260 --> 00:40:00,560
In 4th Prince's dessert

797
00:40:00,660 --> 00:40:02,819
I added something that the others didn't have.

798
00:40:02,919 --> 00:40:04,291
What?

799
00:40:04,540 --> 00:40:06,040
Salt.

800
00:40:06,263 --> 00:40:07,534
Salt?

801
00:40:09,500 --> 00:40:10,639
I was just thinking,

802
00:40:10,780 --> 00:40:12,337
no wonder 4th Brother was swallowing the tea

803
00:40:12,337 --> 00:40:14,252
and not sipping the tea.

804
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:15,438
By the gods,

805
00:40:15,713 --> 00:40:16,983
you are really bold to...

806
00:40:17,083 --> 00:40:18,337
even dare to make fun of 4th Brother,

807
00:40:18,477 --> 00:40:20,280
also right in front of Imperial Father.

808
00:40:20,380 --> 00:40:21,574
Who asked him to tease me all the time?

809
00:40:21,574 --> 00:40:22,576
And also,

810
00:40:22,576 --> 00:40:23,847
if I don't do it in front of His Majesty,

811
00:40:23,847 --> 00:40:25,762
how could I succeed?

812
00:40:28,113 --> 00:40:29,491
He's here!

813
00:40:30,017 --> 00:40:30,988
I'm going.

814
00:40:31,980 --> 00:40:32,980
Had the courage to do it,

815
00:40:32,980 --> 00:40:34,166
so don't run away.

816
00:40:34,266 --> 00:40:35,486
He must still be angry about it.

817
00:40:35,486 --> 00:40:36,979
Let me hide first.

818
00:40:37,260 --> 00:40:38,346
Go.

819
00:40:38,446 --> 00:40:39,924
Come back here!

820
00:40:57,540 --> 00:40:59,240
Want to fight or punish as you want,

821
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:01,149
but don't keep me in suspense.

822
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:03,321
Hand.

823
00:41:16,600 --> 00:41:18,782
You are not afraid of me now?

824
00:41:19,708 --> 00:41:22,108
Since when am I afraid of you?

825
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:25,509
Before,

826
00:41:25,509 --> 00:41:28,360
I had been scared a little bit

827
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,935
Only a little bit.

828
00:41:30,900 --> 00:41:32,150
A little bit more.

829
00:41:32,150 --> 00:41:34,561
Only a little bit more.

830
00:41:35,444 --> 00:41:36,526
Seems that I have to make you

831
00:41:36,526 --> 00:41:38,548
fear me a bit more.

832
00:41:45,140 --> 00:41:46,869
Are you really mad?

833
00:41:48,152 --> 00:41:49,981
You ignore me?

834
00:41:50,740 --> 00:41:53,314
In the future, I won't make fun of you.

835
00:41:54,220 --> 00:41:56,134
I am not angry.

836
00:41:56,534 --> 00:41:58,410
Then why don't you speak?

837
00:41:59,181 --> 00:42:00,524
I'm thirsty.

838
00:42:12,880 --> 00:42:13,924
It makes a long time that I haven't see JieJie

839
00:42:13,924 --> 00:42:15,560
for so long.

840
00:42:15,780 --> 00:42:16,914
Is that so?

841
00:42:17,014 --> 00:42:19,122
There is even laughter in your eyes.

842
00:42:24,500 --> 00:42:26,360
When was last time I smiled...

843
00:42:26,460 --> 00:42:28,778
like this?

844
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:33,481
Kneel down, servant!

845
00:42:35,420 --> 00:42:36,626
Crown Prince.

846
00:42:36,726 --> 00:42:38,098
You... what you want is the tribute wine.

847
00:42:38,098 --> 00:42:40,295
I got all that I could get

848
00:42:40,395 --> 00:42:41,806
So what if it is tribute wine?

849
00:42:41,906 --> 00:42:42,603
Even me, a Crown Prince,

850
00:42:42,603 --> 00:42:44,160
cannot drink it?

851
00:42:44,260 --> 00:42:45,200
Take him away.

852
00:42:45,200 --> 00:42:46,400
Whip him harshly!

853
00:42:46,500 --> 00:42:47,520
Yes.

854
00:42:47,620 --> 00:42:49,280
