- Go!

855
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:49,871
You don't listen to me!

856
00:42:49,871 --> 00:42:51,307
I'll beat you until you listen to me!

857
00:42:51,307 --> 00:42:54,557
If you don't obey me, I will beat you until you obey me!

858
00:43:00,620 --> 00:43:01,886
What is going on?

859
00:43:02,460 --> 00:43:03,965
The Crown Prince is having a banquet today.

860
00:43:03,965 --> 00:43:05,640
He thinks that the wine given to him isn't quite enough.

861
00:43:06,140 --> 00:43:08,075
So he took his anger out on the servants.

862
00:43:08,075 --> 00:43:09,600
Is it always like this?

863
00:43:09,700 --> 00:43:11,063
The rumors of removing the Crown Prince are spreading fast...

864
00:43:11,063 --> 00:43:12,146
and furious throughout the palace.

865
00:43:12,464 --> 00:43:14,320
The Crown Prince has become more agitated.

866
00:43:14,420 --> 00:43:15,560
He always vents his frustration...

867
00:43:15,660 --> 00:43:18,360
on us, servants.

868
00:43:18,460 --> 00:43:19,620
Let him be.

869
00:43:19,620 --> 00:43:21,698
His life isn't going well.

870
00:43:21,798 --> 00:43:22,913
"He" is the Crown Prince!

871
00:43:22,913 --> 00:43:25,095
How can he not be doing well?

872
00:43:26,460 --> 00:43:27,680
Jie Jie.

873
00:43:27,680 --> 00:43:28,530
Could it be...

874
00:43:28,530 --> 00:43:30,460
like the rumours...

875
00:43:30,460 --> 00:43:32,247
