876
00:43:32,247 --> 00:43:33,833
We, who are servants,

877
00:43:33,933 --> 00:43:35,694
have things that we cannot freely tell others.

878
00:43:36,241 --> 00:43:38,045
Jie Jie's reminder is correct.

879
00:43:38,145 --> 00:43:39,020
Oh, Jie Jie,

880
00:43:39,020 --> 00:43:40,856
