881
00:43:41,674 --> 00:43:43,168
Its the Mid-Autumn Festival,

882
00:43:43,168 --> 00:43:45,111
I'm going to go enjoy the moon.

883
00:44:20,340 --> 00:44:21,782
Good in horse-back archery,

884
