885
00:44:23,424 --> 00:44:25,135
He rides the horse swiftly.

886
00:44:25,235 --> 00:44:26,117
His writing is...

887
00:44:26,117 --> 00:44:28,303
neat and refreshing.

888
00:44:28,672 --> 00:44:30,007
His music is...

889
00:44:30,007 --> 00:44:32,379
