894
00:44:48,501 --> 00:44:50,050
Why don't you continue?

895
00:44:50,150 --> 00:44:51,582
Did I disturb you?

896
00:44:51,682 --> 00:44:52,843
Just felt like someone was secretly listening,

897
00:44:52,843 --> 00:44:55,408
I didn't know it was you, that's why I stopped.

898
00:44:56,380 --> 00:44:57,968
Why didn't you stay by His Majesty's side,

899
